===Etymology===
:Compound of ''[[sun]]'' + ''[[rise]]''

===Noun===
'''sunrise''' (''plural:'' [[sunrises]])

#The [[time]] of [[day]] when the [[sun]] [[appear]]s above the [[eastern]] [[horizon]].
#The [[change]] in [[color]] of the [[sky]] at sunrise.

